      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REACT TO BEAUTY (7) worked to get to the lead and kept finding to salute last start over 1800m at Globe Derby Park after a sequence of minor placings recently. Drawn to enjoy a cosy run but might need things to go his way at some stage. It doesn't get any easier but he is good enough to take this out. WHATA OPTIMIST (8) finished fourth last start over 1790m at Ararat, beaten 25 metres, after a good win at Shepparton the run prior. Ideally placed and is sure to play a major role. EMRITES (9) disappointed last time when eighth over 1800m at Globe Derby Park. Is better than that and can turn things around. TRIGGER (5) must be included on the back of some solid recent form, most recently when fourth at Globe Derby Park over 1800m.",
